law.history: Repealed 2004 Ky. Acts ch. 36, sec. 36, effective July 13, 2004. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 485, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1994. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 349, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1988. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 90, sec. 27, effective July 15, 1986.
